name: 'To the Victor the Spoils'
description:
Digital version of an original oil on wood painting. JPEG 4084 x 2982 pixels @ 150 dpi.

This is the second work in the 'trophies' series which explore themes of nostalgia, value, masculinity, and renaissance artefacts. Each painting is based on an original 3D model made from found objects and miniature figurines.
